snippet.title: "Impossible Island" Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
"Impossbile Island" by Studio Gathering Studio is an open world building and survival game where you play as a pirate.

The project, which was recently released as early access on steam, continues to be developed and prepared for full release.

You can use this link to reach the game

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2950820/Impossible_Island/

Social media

Website: https://studiogatheringstorm.com/
